recognizing right...

01:59:22.360 --> 01:59:24.851
...as well as reality."

01:59:26.130 --> 01:59:29.293
Today, 30 years later...

01:59:29.634 --> 01:59:31.966
...on behalf of the state
of Mississippi...

01:59:32.170 --> 01:59:36.971
...I'm asking you 12 ladies
